Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.57,0:23:19.60,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}讓脈搏合奏出旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.81,0:23:23.27,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}做想做的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------正文--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.02,0:01:50.01,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}蹴鞠頭兒再襲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.35,0:02:03.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  搞什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.31,0:02:05.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有驚無險嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.40,0:02:09.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  圭子  考得怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.19,0:02:10.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.44,0:02:13.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,65分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.35,0:02:15.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來都準備好亮紅燈了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.08,0:02:17.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣還算過得去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.75,0:02:18.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.59,0:02:20.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  圭子你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.55,0:02:26.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一…一百
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.86,0:02:33.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總共一百分你全拿到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.77,0:02:35.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說「百發百中」了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.88,0:02:39.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說沒有失誤了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.33,0:02:40.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說很完美了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.14,0:02:42.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.44,0:02:43.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在是太無聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.12,0:02:45.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是無趣的分數
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.12,0:02:47.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼擅長計算的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.54,0:02:48.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就去當個計算器好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.93,0:02:49.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這計算器
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.58,0:02:53.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不必說得這麼過分吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.62,0:02:55.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與此相比  65分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.14,0:02:58.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才像是人該得的分數
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.77,0:03:01.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和計算器比試也太無聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.71,0:03:04.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有棋逢對手的傢伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.27,0:03:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  南同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.24,0:03:07.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考得怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.94,0:03:08.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了啊  頭兒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.42,0:03:11.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又想向我挑戰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.72,0:03:13.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？頭兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.00,0:03:16.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  你打算用什麼分數來和我較量呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.77,0:03:17.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是說出來聽聽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.61,0:03:19.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  我會輕而易舉地擊敗你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.72,0:03:21.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆些說出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.41,0:03:23.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  不…我不是想較量什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.07,0:03:26.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,66分
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.00,0:03:30.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岡同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.24,0:03:32.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不必說得那麼過分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:36.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才說了什麼很過分的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.92,0:03:38.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  還沒完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.63,0:03:39.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒輸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.10,0:03:41.58,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fs27}迄今戰績
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.58,0:03:42.79,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fs27}一勝一負
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.13,0:03:44.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你之間的戰績才不過是一勝一負
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.33,0:03:46.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別以為你贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.18,0:03:49.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  我什麼時候輸的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:51.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以英語考試的成績來決勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.90,0:03:53.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…可以倒是可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.11,0:03:55.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fsp128}　{\fsp1}Penalty{\r}\N那麼來約定一下處罰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.20,0:03:58.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰輸了就得裝狗  如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.72,0:04:00.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說夏奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.12,0:04:02.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  好的  那就這麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.31,0:04:04.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可別想溜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.57,0:04:06.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會讓你乖乖伸爪子的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.57,0:04:06.16,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（注：原文「お手」，训狗用的口令）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.09,0:04:10.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這就差不多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.86,0:04:13.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便問下  圭子你考得如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.50,0:04:15.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？呃…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:21.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一百…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.82,0:04:24.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去美國過活算了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.84,0:04:28.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,61分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.69,0:04:31.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是個人情味兒十足的美妙分數
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.25,0:04:35.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可剛才65分也還是輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.94,0:04:39.40,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fs27}篡改
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.00,0:04:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來  那傢伙剛才是66分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.37,0:04:49.33,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fs27}篡改  Ⅱ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.46,0:04:54.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南同學  怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.16,0:04:56.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來了啊  藤岡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:04:58.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先讓我看看你的分數吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.57,0:04:59.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,69分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.05,0:05:01.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.11,0:05:05.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧你還改了兩次分數…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.51,0:05:08.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？我贏了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.69,0:05:09.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.49,0:05:10.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.96,0:05:12.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比試這才開始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.11,0:05:13.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.36,0:05:23.22,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fs27}篡改  Ⅲ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:28.22,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(880,870)}一百
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.88,0:05:40.17,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fs27}篡改  Ⅳ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.76,0:05:45.18,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(960,920)}一百
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.76,0:05:52.19,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(910,920)\fs27}午休（午餐供應）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.94,0:06:08.24,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fs27}篡改  Ⅴ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.74,0:06:12.21,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(960,920)}一百
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.57,0:06:19.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又…又輸了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.09,0:06:22.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改了這麼多次分數還…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.44,0:06:24.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我贏了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.16,0:06:26.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  說好了的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:28.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸爪子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.97,0:06:37.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南同學  那可是腳…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.22,0:06:41.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然叫做「前腳」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.97,0:06:42.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼爪子也是腳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.23,0:06:44.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳也是腳！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.66,0:06:45.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.55,0:06:47.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.38,0:06:54.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.91,0:06:56.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想冒昧一問
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.90,0:06:57.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.08,0:07:02.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近  在學校的考試成績如何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.77,0:07:07.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這蝦黃醬口味的餅乾很好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.57,0:07:18.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.07,0:07:29.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼搪塞我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:33.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為覺得這話題發展下去準沒什麼好結果
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:36.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可…不見得…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.30,0:07:50.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙實在太差勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.97,0:07:54.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為只要不是一百就有人情味兒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.84,0:08:04.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把人家的牛奶喝個精光還反過來說我「差勁」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.89,0:08:06.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然沒什麼好結果
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.35,0:08:18.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就一筆勾銷了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.23,0:08:19.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼一筆勾銷了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.32,0:08:22.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒有輸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.44,0:08:24.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是考試成績不好？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:26.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.27,0:08:29.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是包含人間溫情的美好的分數
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.79,0:08:35.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別因為自己考了97分就得意洋洋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.22,0:08:38.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭子她還考了一百呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.49,0:08:39.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你又是多少分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.64,0:08:42.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我喝光你的牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.91,0:09:09.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼樣  見識到我的可怕之處了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.92,0:09:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:16.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fsp254}　{\fsp1}Cream Stew{\r}\N春香姐姐可是說了今晚要做奶油雜燴的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.36,0:09:16.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.23,0:09:21.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上還滿滿的一盒到傍晚就一乾二淨了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.84,0:09:24.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概姐姐她也沒想到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.64,0:09:26.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我去買總行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.01,0:09:36.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.06,0:09:40.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子裏的牛奶晃蕩得好噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.78,0:09:43.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛奶這蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.31,0:09:45.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.34,0:09:50.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  怎麼著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.82,0:09:54.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為千秋你總是狡詐地學啊學的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.47,0:09:56.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說什麼狡詐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:09:59.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷偷摸摸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.43,0:10:02.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你分數就那麼差嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:05.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說不是差了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:09.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是一個通情達理真心實意的分數
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.79,0:10:16.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指望以抱佛腳換來好分數的想法本身就有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.62,0:10:21.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就只能說出這麼大眾化的意見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.74,0:10:22.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.29,0:10:25.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將來娶你的男人還真是不幸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.23,0:10:27.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.89,0:10:30.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被這種大眾化意見所掩埋的新婚生活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.15,0:10:32.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不可能會有趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.05,0:10:36.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別憑自己的妄想斷言別人的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.93,0:10:38.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就單說做飯也是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.83,0:10:42.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本就無法做出讓人感動的飯菜來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.71,0:10:45.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能感動也無所謂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.35,0:10:51.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你的夫婿就將這麼結束沒有感動的不幸的一生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.86,0:10:54.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能做出來對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.05,0:10:55.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.99,0:11:00.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非比尋常的你應該能做出讓人感動的飯菜來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.28,0:11:02.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是當然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.28,0:11:08.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  你去做給我看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.40,0:11:12.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯  讓你品嚐一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.92,0:11:16.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論何時  能夠創造出新奇食物的不是常識
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.45,0:11:18.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是那瞬間的靈感
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.74,0:11:19.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.63,0:11:24.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬間的靈感上回孕育出了慘不忍睹的奶油雜燴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.25,0:11:25.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你忘記了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.49,0:11:35.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:39.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  對不起  已經等不及了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.05,0:11:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們做了什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.73,0:11:42.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Gratin　{\r}\N奶汁烤菜？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.83,0:11:43.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天麩羅？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.83,0:11:43.50,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（註：日式食品，裹上麵粉後油炸的魚蝦之類）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.80,0:11:45.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Paella{\r}\N還是西班牙海鮮飯呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.95,0:11:47.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫你做奶油雜燴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.77,0:11:48.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去買牛奶來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.51,0:11:57.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.09,0:12:05.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝者  春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.06,0:12:07.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.82,0:12:11.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區一介奶油雜燴也能使人心蕩神馳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.47,0:12:51.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？什麼時候睡著的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.36,0:12:54.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.37,0:12:58.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙  想報仇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.81,0:13:00.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然趁我睡著時偷襲  太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.88,0:13:02.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂堂正正地來比試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:06.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.71,0:13:09.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一堂課要改去音樂教室上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.59,0:13:11.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你卻在這兒睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.90,0:13:13.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本想叫醒你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.53,0:13:15.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可看你睡得很舒服就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.36,0:13:17.34,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（下節課  音樂教室）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.80,0:13:20.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真是很可疑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.90,0:13:23.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  也無所謂就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.50,0:13:28.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  南同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.08,0:13:29.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.02,0:13:31.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次好像並沒有很好地傳達給你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.11,0:13:33.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就直說了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.00,0:13:34.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.76,0:13:37.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.37,0:13:39.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.70,0:13:41.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.17,0:13:43.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.71,0:13:57.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.60,0:13:58.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋大小姐回來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.42,0:14:01.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何事  甚是吵嚷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.58,0:14:02.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.54,0:14:05.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有些事想和您談談
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.79,0:14:06.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.69,0:14:10.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天在學校頭兒對我說「我很喜歡你」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.28,0:14:13.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前他不還給我寫了情書嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.04,0:14:16.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是怎麼一回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.92,0:14:20.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是喜歡你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:23.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼傻話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.94,0:14:27.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我太得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.84,0:14:30.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  他是在什麼情況下對你說的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.04,0:14:38.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙  想報仇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.53,0:14:42.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在教室裏睡著了  而他好像想偷襲我的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.06,0:14:45.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我就對他說「堂堂正正地來比試吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.23,0:14:47.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.87,0:14:48.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.61,0:14:52.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說你因為在睡夢中被偷襲而情緒不穩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.91,0:14:55.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後又因為他出人意料的話語而心神不寧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.34,0:14:59.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,導致思考回路短路了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.79,0:15:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是怎麼一回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.45,0:15:06.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的大腦在聽到「很喜歡」的那一刻就停止工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.61,0:15:14.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭兒後來應該還說了些什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.96,0:15:17.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一說  好像確實…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.82,0:15:18.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從當時的情況推測的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.07,0:15:20.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕當時他是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.67,0:15:23.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「你那架勢滿是破綻」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.67,0:15:23.35,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（註：此句發音的前半部分和「很喜歡」這句一樣）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.22,0:15:33.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太難為情了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:37.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然三番兩次地會錯意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.16,0:15:39.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感到飢渴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.34,0:15:40.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在追求什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.63,0:15:43.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那所謂的告白之類酸酸甜甜的什麼東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.63,0:15:46.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這麼一來就清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:47.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清楚我們應該採取何種對策了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:57.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來  今天足球部有練習嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.27,0:15:58.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.45,0:16:03.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.63,0:16:04.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.34,0:16:07.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一節是數學課哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.41,0:16:08.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作業做了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.91,0:16:10.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  什麼作業？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.60,0:16:12.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南同學  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.95,0:16:40.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被討厭了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:45.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.00,0:16:51.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.55,0:16:51.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.13,0:16:56.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你好  打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.24,0:17:00.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…你好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.22,0:17:05.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我買飲料回來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.93,0:17:06.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.06,0:17:08.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.61,0:17:10.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  千秋  歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.44,0:17:12.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙就是藤岡啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.18,0:17:14.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岡？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.82,0:17:15.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個頭兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.44,0:17:19.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼頭兒會在咱家？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.52,0:17:21.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.76,0:17:26.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是想和他大幹一場然後取而代之
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.71,0:17:29.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也希望能避免無謂的紛爭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.69,0:17:30.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.85,0:17:32.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天不是咖喱做多了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.34,0:17:34.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:43.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？怎麼稀得像水一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.89,0:17:45.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fsp32}　{\fsp1}Curry Roux{\r}\N再加些咖喱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.84,0:17:53.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？這次就太稠了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.88,0:17:55.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就只能弄稀一些了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.14,0:18:02.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？覺得又稀了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.45,0:18:05.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加些咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.13,0:18:07.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又太稠了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.07,0:18:09.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就只好加水了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.97,0:18:11.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太稀了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.47,0:18:12.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.95,0:18:13.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太稠了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.08,0:18:14.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加水
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.98,0:18:24.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼最後會做出三大鍋咖喱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.57,0:18:31.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用做多了的咖喱和頭兒套關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.32,0:18:34.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是一石二鳥的好法子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.16,0:18:37.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後他就這麼跟著你來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.13,0:18:38.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.34,0:18:42.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本還以為南同學討厭我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.71,0:18:44.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像並不是這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.96,0:18:45.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.02,0:18:49.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不僅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.98,0:18:51.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她還請我上家裏來吃晚飯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.19,0:18:52.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.72,0:18:54.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離一下子就拉近了不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.70,0:18:55.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  給你茶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.14,0:19:00.85,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（舉止可疑）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.52,0:19:05.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這人一定在打什麼鬼主意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.11,0:19:07.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.11,0:19:11.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.96,0:19:13.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  說笑的說笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.64,0:19:15.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.08,0:19:19.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說啊  春香姐姐做的咖喱可是非常好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.43,0:19:23.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼  有意見你倒是別吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.53,0:19:28.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  剩下兩大鍋你打算自己吃完？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.71,0:19:32.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  是小的出言不遜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.85,0:19:38.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岡同學不是個挺好的孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.81,0:19:41.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  他居然會是頭兒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.59,0:19:42.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是有什麼誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.65,0:19:45.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且該怎麼說好呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.95,0:19:48.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他給人的感覺酷似爸爸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.08,0:19:49.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.69,0:19:57.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸給人的感覺是那樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.89,0:20:01.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二宮同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.01,0:20:02.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.28,0:20:07.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.01,0:20:09.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二宮同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.02,0:20:12.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師～！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.50,0:20:14.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二宮同學！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.67,0:20:17.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師和二宮同學後續如何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.39,0:20:18.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬請下周繼續收看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.67,0:20:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  已經這麼晚了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.77,0:20:24.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我差不多得回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.61,0:20:31.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  這可不像千秋你的作風哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:34.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼想說的話就說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.18,0:20:36.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兒是我的位子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.31,0:20:38.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.23,0:20:40.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.08,0:20:54.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.61,0:20:57.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.31,0:21:01.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來  藤岡同學參加了什麼社團嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.09,0:21:04.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我參加了足球部
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.69,0:21:06.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  足球部啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.41,0:21:08.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踢什麼位置呢  是主力嗎
